<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.545747>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13 – 18. Male of Trichuris mallomyos sp. nov. collected from Mallomys rothschildi in Papua, Indonesia. 13. Holotype. 14. Middle portion of stichosome showing bacillary band at left side. 15. Enlarged view at middle showing surface of bacillary band partially; two-way arrow indicating width of bacillary band at this level. 16. Caudal end. 17. Distal end of spicule; arrows showing pit-like structures. 18. Distal end of spicular sheath fully extended." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/545747/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.545748>
    dc:description "FIGURES 19 – 22. Female of Trichuris musseri sp. nov. collected from Mallomys rothschildi in Papua Indonesia. 19. Allotype. 20. Esopahgo-intestinal junction. 21. Caudal end. 22. Egg." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/545748/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

